name: JuiceboxDAO
description: Supports projects built using the Juicebox protocol, and the development of the protocol itself. All projects withdrawing funds from their treasury pay a 5% membership fee and receive JBX at the current issuance rate. JBX members govern the NFT that represents ownership over this treasury.
